    "The anti-time-ordered amplitude M † appears because the continuation lands on the \"wrong\" side of the cut.",
    "In a forthcoming paper, we will propose that a certain analytic continuation of the five-point conjugated scattering amplitude M † 12→345 yields precisely the inclusive expectation value (1.3) [10], see figure 1.",
